    dc:description "FIGURE 28. Distributional map of type localites of Elasmopus yupanquii sp. nov., E. incarocai sp. nov., E. yahuarhuaci sp. nov., E. viracochai sp. nov. and E. pachacuteci sp. nov. Map Symbols: Diamond (Type locality of E. pachacuteci sp. nov and E. viracochai sp. nov). Circle (Type locality of E. yupanchii sp. nov.). Square (Type locality of E. yahuarhuaci sp. nov.). Star (Type locality of E. incarocai sp. nov.)." ;
